Title: #136 Jubilee Singers: Sacrifice and Glory
Description: A group of former slaves tries to save its bankrupt school by performing concerts as the Jubilee Singers.   Episode #136

Title: s02e22 Penguin Keeper
Description: While they may seem cute and cuddly, penguins create a lot of very smelly waste which Mike discovers when he heads to Audubon Zoo in New Orleans to work as a keeper for the day.   Season 02, Episode 22

Title: s03e03 Mule Logger
Description: Mike gets his hands dirty digging tunnels that are used as underground wine caverns; then he meets some loggers who use mules to drag their felled trees away.   Season 03, Episode 03

Title: s06e25 Fossil Hunter
Description: Mike takes on his latest challenge, traveling to Utah to take on the surprisingly dirty job of being a paleontologist.   Season 06, Episode 25

Title: s06e27 Water Softener Technician
Description: Mike tries his hand at working as a water softener technician; Mike takes on the job of a coin washer.   Season 06, Episode 27

Title: s06e28 Barber's Assistant
Description: Mike learns some of the tricks of the haircutting trade; Mike spends the day working as a landfill operator.   Season 06, Episode 28

Title: s06e29 Mardi Gras Bladder Banger
Description: Mike spends the day in Mobile, Ala. assembling cow bladders that will be used during a Mardi Gras parade.   Season 06, Episode 29

Title: s06e30 Medical Waste
Description: Mike samples life as a medical waste processor, learning what medical waste is and then doing his bit to treat it; his new colleagues have some surprises in store.   Season 06, Episode 30

Title: s06e31 Tower Top Hand
Description: Mike helps to erect a radio communications tower; celebrating the milestone of doing a dirty job in each of the 50 states.   Season 06, Episode 31

Title: #167 Closing In
Description: Excitement grows when the team discovers a 200-year-old searcher shaft which could lead them directly to the Money Pit.   Episode #167

Title: s40e07 Westerly: The Doors
Description: Building a section of a coffered ceiling; cutting granite; septic system; how interior doors are built; installing a door.   Season 40, Episode 07
